	  src/vpn-manager/nm-vpn-connection.c
	  src/NetworkManagerPolicy.c
		- Fix up for NMSettingConnection 'name'->'id' changes

2007-11-13  Dan Williams  <dcbw@redhat.com>

	* libnm-glib/nm-device-802-11-wireless.h
