2007-09-11  Dan Williams  <dcbw@redhat.com>

	* libnm-util/nm-setting.c
	  libnm-util/nm-setting.h
		- (nm_setting_update_secrets): new function; add a virtual function that
			subclasses can implement to update their secrets
