		- (supplicant_monitor_start): increase connect/auth timeout to
			20 seconds from 10 seconds

2006-01-30  Dan Williams  <dcbw@redhat.com>

	* src/Makefile.am
		- Define LOCALSTATEDIR

	* src/nm-device-802-11-wireless.c
